node.text: It blows my mind that age, gender and skin colour are all irrelevant when it comes to the Sickick Army. So many different walks of life appreciating the same bodies of work, and in turn feeding the movement to be that much stronger. Each one of you make a difference to my life everyday, and I don’t want y’all to forget that. Infect someone new with the sickness today and stay S!CK. #sickestdj #spreadthesickness #reaction
